   File Name		Description
-----------------------------------------------------------
README	         	- A short introduction.
MANIFEST	 	- A list of files.
dot.fonts.conf		- X11 fontconfig config file.
dot.gtkrc		- X11 GTK-based config file.
dot.Xdefaults		- X11 applications's default action.
dot.muttrc		- A mail client program(mutt)'s config file.
dot.vimrc		- A editor(vim)'s config file.
dot.xinitrc		- When X11 Server start, what it should do.
dot.bashrc		- A shell(bash)'s config file.
dot.cshrc		- A shell(csh/tcsh)'s config file.
dot.inputrc		- For input of 8 bit character.
dot.emacs		- A editor(Emacs)'s config file.
make.conf		- Global settings for compile, install software.
			  Please copy this file tp /etc and modify for your needs.
